{"tid":1426860,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[和理非進場]仲有罷買可做","createTime":"2019-08-07T04:07:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T10:18:27.000Z","uid":32469,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0d9f3c643ec0676b7fb77eb07f72af3656c9a126","tid":1426860,"uid":32469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:07:03.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">首先！！</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7EHKDk2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7EHKDk2.png&h=0b13c30c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之前我有提及過和理非行動嘅重要性，詳情睇返以下個po<br />\n<br />\n統戰和理非及勇武之拙見<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1417737\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1417737</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除左機場集會之外，我想提提<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">罷買</span></span></strong>。呢個和理非行動<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">成本低，效益高</span></span></strong>，亦可以吸引大批和理非參與。<br />\n<br />\n我認為罷買係個可以<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">長期而規律</span></span></strong>進行嘅抗爭。例如每星期特定日子罷買，淨係搭車同三餐用錢。開頭每星期一日，再好似之前咁set deadline之後升級，變成每星期兩日、三日、四日。另外可以加插特別抵制出聲反示威嘅企業/有支持紅底嘅企業，例如重提抵制cctvb落廣告，吉野家嘅行動。做返我地之前嘅行動，比和理非有用之地。<br />\n<br />\n而呢個行動需要各位巴打做文宣號召，亦需要時間蘊釀先會夠力。但小弟不才，唔識出設，尤有係到建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4825e19476cec35d8bb6385eb9d6890b97dd20c9","tid":1426860,"uid":32469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:13:57.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e95d336c53434511b53d097a66517d16ef0d1578","tid":1426860,"uid":32469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:14:08.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"82e5d734f21ddb7a3d260bbbe6bdd640250a4ce2","tid":1426860,"uid":32469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:15:20.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e27753a6e5e32f83121e2ad0af476910f833b92d","tid":1426860,"uid":32469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:16:15.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2e6c53dc852980974542a7e17bb30701dfb740d6","tid":1426860,"uid":32469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:16:27.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4049fa01cc062c424ca1c550a167a3ce955c45e1","tid":1426860,"uid":32469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:16:38.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"21a45f72d350d71b0b595b19864cbf39111a5160","tid":1426860,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:18:27.000Z","msg":"推"}]}